布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀谈杰里米·艾伦·怀特传记片的选角：“我知道他是合适的人选” https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-cast-in-传记片-我知道他是对的人Surej SinghTue, 29 Oct 2024 04:00:35 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3807303 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>昨天分享了怀特扮演老板的第一眼</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 关于杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 传记片选角的帖子：“我知道他是合适的人选”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>分享了他对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeremy-allen-white">杰里米·艾伦·怀特</a>在即将上映的传记片<em>《从无处拯救我》</em>中扮演“老板”的想法。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944"><b>生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</b></a></li></ul><p>昨天（10 月 28 日）， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><em>《熊》</em></a>主演杰里米·艾伦·怀特饰演年轻的布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-transforms-into-bruce-springsteen-in-first-look-at-new-biopic-3806993">首次正式</a>亮相。在下面的图片中，怀特穿着 The Boss 标志性的法兰绒和牛仔夹克造型，双手插在口袋里。</p><p>在最近接受<a href="https://www.telegraph.co.uk/music/interviews/bruce-springsteen-interview-trump-is-mentally-unstable/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《每日电讯报》</em></a>采访时，斯普林斯汀被问及怀特的选角问题。老板回复道，解释怀特是这个角色的“合适人选”：“我只在<em>《熊》</em>中看到了他，我就知道他是合适的人选，因为他有那种内心生活，但他也有一点狂妄。 ”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807026" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807026" style="width: 1999px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807026" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere.jpg" alt="杰里米·艾伦·怀特在《从无处拯救我》中饰演布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀" width="1999" height="3000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere.jpg 1999w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-400x600.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-800x1201.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-696x1045.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-1392x2089.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Jeremy-Allen-White-as-Bruce-Springsteen-in-Deliver-Me-From-Nowhere-1068x1603.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807026" class="wp-caption-text">杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 在《从无处拯救我》中饰演布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen)。图片来源：华特迪士尼工作室</figcaption></figure><p>斯普林斯汀的长期导师兼经理乔恩·兰道补充说，扮演“老板”会看到怀特“描绘出一个非常内向的人。总是有大量的事情在发生，其中一些被阐明，而另一些则被抑制。”</p><p>在影片中，兰道将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/succession"><em>《继承之战</em></a>》的杰里米·斯特朗饰演。此后，兰多与斯特朗交谈，并向他提供了以下建议：“我确实告诉他，就他的体重而言，他不需要在角色发展上完全融入《愤怒的公牛》。”斯普林斯汀插话，开玩笑说电影制片人“试图让[斯特朗]穿上肥大的衣服”。</p><p>怀特在<em>《无处可逃》</em>中饰演斯普林斯汀的消息<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeremy-allen-white-to-reportedly-play-bruce-springsteen-in-nebraska-film-3615030">最早是在四月份报道的</a>。这部电影定于明年上映，将探讨斯普林斯汀 1982 年标志性专辑《内布拉斯加》的制作过程。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805279" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805279" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805279" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/bruce-springsteen-jon-landau-jim-spellman-1-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805279" class="wp-caption-text">纽约，纽约 – 5 月 6 日：歌手/词曲作者 Bruce Springsteen 和音乐制作人 Jon Landau 出席 2017 年 5 月 6 日在纽约市 Tribeca Grill 举行的 2017 年 Kristen Ann Carr 基金“难忘之夜”晚会。 （吉姆·斯佩尔曼/盖蒂图片社拍摄）</figcaption></figure><p>除了《White and Strong》之外， <em>《Deliver Me From Nowhere》</em>还将由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/stephen-graham-cast-as-bruce-springsteens-dad-in-new-biopic-deliver-me-from-nowhere-3797885"><em>《浴血黑帮》的</em>史蒂文·格雷厄姆</a>饰演斯普林斯汀的父亲， <em>《黑鸟》的</em>保罗·沃尔特·豪瑟将饰演吉他技术人员迈克·巴特兰。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/bruce-springsteens-manager-says-jeremy-allen-white-is-perfect-choice-to-lead-biopic-3805265">最近，现实生活中的兰道在谈到怀特的表演时</a>告诉<em><a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movies/movie-news/bruce-springsteen-manager-jon-landau-jeremy-allen-white-biopic-1236040849/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《好莱坞报道》</a> ：</em> “天哪，他太完美了。选角很棒。 [导演]斯科特[库珀]一开始就对我说，‘我们找到了合适的演员，我们会正确地讲述这个故事’，他找到了合适的演员。”</p><p>八月，怀特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-says-bruce-springsteen-biopic-prep-includes-going-down-a-youtube-rabbit-hole-3788125">谈到了为这个角色做的准备</a>，他解释道：“我真的很幸运，现在有一个团队可以帮助年轻演员扮演摇滚明星。我有一群非常有才华的人帮助我训练声音和音乐，为这件事做好准备。” </p><div class="td_block_wrap tdb_single_content tdi_86 td-pb-border-top td_block_template_2 td-post-content tagdiv-type" data-td-block-uid="tdi_86" data-io-article-url="https://www.nme.com/news/film/jeremy-allen-white-transforms-into-bruce-springsteen-in-first-look-at-new-biopic-3806993"><div class="tdb-block-inner td-fix-index"><p>他补充说，斯普林斯汀“非常支持这个项目”，并称这位摇滚偶像“只是最伟大的人”。</p></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-on-jeremy-allen-whites-casting-in-biopic-i-knew-he-was-the-right-guy-3807303">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 (Bruce Springsteen) 关于杰里米·艾伦·怀特 (Jeremy Allen White) 传记片选角的帖子：“我知道他是合适的人选”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Kid Rock 分享了他对泰勒·斯威夫特和阿姆支持卡玛拉·哈里斯的看法https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-shares-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=kid-摇滚分享他对泰勒·斯威夫特和阿姆认可卡马拉·哈里斯的想法Surej SinghTue, 29 Oct 2024 03:14:35 +0000 Music NewsNewsDonald TrumpKamala HarrisPoliticsPopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3807296 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>自 2016 年以来一直是唐纳德·特朗普的直言不讳的支持者的洛克说：“以不同的方式思考并拥有这样做的自由是这个国家变得伟大的原因。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kid-rock-shares-his-thoughts-on-taylor-swift-and-eminem-endorsing-kamala-harris-3807296">摇滚小子 (Kid Rock) 分享了他对泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 和阿姆 (Eminem) 代言卡玛拉·哈里斯 (Kamala Harris) 的看法，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/eminem-kid-rock-taylor-swift@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kid-rock">Kid Rock</a>谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eminem">阿姆</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>支持<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/kamala-harris">卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>竞选美国总统 - 看看这位说唱歌手在下面怎么说。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/eminem-the-death-of-slim-shady-coup-de-grace-album-review-3774875">埃米纳姆 – 《The Death of Slim Shady (Coup De Grâce)》评论：精心制作的歌曲和空洞的挑衅</a></strong></li></ul><p>九月，泰勒·斯威夫特<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-announces-endorsement-of-kamala-harris-for-president-3792514">宣布支持卡玛拉·哈里斯</a>。埃米纳姆上周<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/obama-raps-lose-yourself-verse-at-kamala-harris-rally-after-being-introduced-by-eminem-3805325">出席哈里斯底特律集会并介绍了前总统巴拉克·奥巴马</a>时证实了他的支持。 </p><figure id="attachment_3807298" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807298" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807298" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/obama-eminem@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807298" class="wp-caption-text">巴拉克·奥巴马和埃米纳姆在卡马拉·哈里斯的底特律集会上。图片来源：DOMINIC GWINN/中东图片/法新社盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>Kid Rock 长期以来一直是<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>的支持者，可以追溯到 2016 年这位前总统的选举。近几个月来，Kid Rock（真名罗伯特“鲍勃”里奇）已经成为特朗普阵营的代言人，并出现在多个场合集会支持共和党候选人。</p><p>自从阿姆出现在哈里斯的集会上后，摇滚小子就在社交媒体上表达了他对阿姆和泰勒·斯威夫特对哈里斯支持的看法。在发布到 X 的一段视频中，可以看到这位乡村说唱歌手赤裸上身弹奏着原声吉他。他停下来说道：“现在我引起了你们的注意，我爱阿姆。我们已经是很多年的朋友了。” </p><figure id="attachment_3807299" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3807299" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3807299" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/donald-trum-kid-rock@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3807299" class="wp-caption-text"> 2018 年唐纳德·特朗普和 Kid Rock。图片来源：SAUL LOEB/AFP via Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Kid Rock 继续说道：“我不同意他的政治观点，但我确实赞扬他和像泰勒·斯威夫特这样的人站出来，并且不害怕为他们所相信的事情发声。以不同的方式思考并拥有这样做的自由才是这个国家的伟大之处。”</p><p>随后，他加大了对特朗普的支持，并补充道：“我的立场是明确的，让美国再次伟大，因为我内心、思想、身体和灵魂都知道，特朗普总统将使美国再次伟大。上帝保佑美国。”</p><blockquote class