jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-payne">利亚姆·佩恩</a>的第一首遗作歌曲将于本周晚些时候发行——了解更多信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-payne-one-direction-obituary-3803755">Liam Payne 1993-2024：One Direction 明星帮助引发了流行现象</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位独唱艺术家和前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/one-direction">One Direction</a>成员于 10 月 16 日<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/one-directions-liam-payne-had-died-aged-31-3803523">从阿根廷布宜诺斯艾利斯卡萨苏尔巴勒莫酒店三楼阳台坠落</a>身亡。阿根廷检察官办公室透露，这名31岁的男子<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-paynes-cause-of-death-and-details-of-hotel-room-in-disarray-revealed-3803859">的死因是多处外伤和内外出血</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3806079" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3806079" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3806079" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/liam-payne@2000x1270-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3806079" class="wp-caption-text">利亚姆·佩恩.图片来源：Hanna Lassen/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>现在，格莱美奖制作人兼歌手萨姆·庞兹（Sam Pounds）在社交媒体上宣布即将发行一首他们共同制作的歌曲，在佩恩不幸去世之前，他一直与佩恩一起在录音室里。</p><p>庞兹写道：“我祈祷这将成为利亚姆一直梦想的世界的祝福。我祈祷天使每天都会在聆听时安慰你们。我祈祷这首歌能够祝福露丝、贝尔和整个家庭。我祈祷这首歌能够消除负面的回响。我祈祷超自然的积极治愈力量将拥抱你们每一个人……带着爱，让我们都成为祝福。”</p><p> Pounds